The article is a proclamation issued by President Donald J. Trump on May 10, 2019, in honor of Mother's Day. The proclamation highlights the importance of mothers in shaping the nation and acknowledges their role in inspiring patriotism and devotion to freedom. It emphasizes the unwavering love and guidance that mothers provide, preparing their children for the challenges of adulthood and helping them reach their full potential. The proclamation encourages all Americans to express their love and respect for their mothers and reflect on the significance of motherhood to the prosperity of families, communities, and the nation.